---
// Replaces the old "Trusted by [fake customers]" strip with an honest banner that
// flags the product as pre-launch and invites Founding Customers. Keeps the visual
// rhythm of the original but tells the truth.
---
<section class="bg-surface-50 border-y border-black/5 py-10">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
    <p class="eyebrow text-prizm-600 mb-2">Now open · Founding Customer program</p>
    <p class="text-navy-900/75 text-base md:text-lg leading-snug">
      We&#39;re onboarding the first cohort of mid-market forwarders, 3PLs, and NVOCCs.
      <span class="hidden sm:inline text-navy-900/55">Founding customers get 40% off their first year and a direct line to the team building the product.</span>
    </p>
    <a href="/request-demo" class="mt-4 inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm font-semibold text-prizm-600 hover:text-prizm-700">
      Apply for Founding Customer access <span aria-hidden>→</span>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>
